END )|| ( CASE WHEN A.SANG_END_DATE IS NULL THEN '0' ELSE '1' END )|| /* 疑い病名が上に表示されない様に注釈処理 ( CASE WHEN NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER1 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER2 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER3 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER4 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER5 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER6 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER7 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER8 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER9 , 'XXXX') = '8002' OR NVL(A.POST_MODIFIER10, 'XXXX') = '8002' THEN '0' ELSE '1' END )|| */ TO_CHAR(A.SANG_START_DATE, 'YYYYMMDD')||LTRIM(TO_CHAR(A.SER, '0000000000')) ORDER_BY_KEY FROM OUTSANG A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho -- 今回の入院時の傷病だけを見せる -- AND A.FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001 -- AND A.GWA = :f_gwa --insert by jc[診療科問わず全部表示させるため] AND A.GWA LIKE :f_gwa AND A.IO_GUBUN = 'I' AND A.SANG_START_DATE <= TO_DATE(:f_naewon_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND NVL(A.SANG_END_DATE,
